ĒóŔRarchive/external_nushell_repo_backup/nushell.github.io/blog/2023-11-04-twin0219.mdŔ@72654db9f6ef63a8b66a1b336f8fb4be348c7cefacabb8e4296d56eb55a77799ĻThis week in Nushell #219ĎßNushellŕschrieveslaach 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10723] implemented an early version of an integrated LSP Server
fdncred 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10936] removed unwraps in registry_query command
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10912] allowed 
``compact``
 to also compact empty strings
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10870] allowed 
``sort-by``
 to work with records
KAAtheWiseGit 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10923] refactored 
``error make``
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10913] changed 
``input list``
 to return null
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10892] changed the category of scope commands to core
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10785] added a 
``umkdir``
 command that uses uutils
stfacc 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10922] added "shape_keyword" to default config
sholderbach 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10917] refactored to use new Record APIs in 
``nu-protocol``
/
``nu-engine``
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10893] converted "pure" macros to pure fn in 
``config.rs``
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10876] added 
``Record::remove``
/
``retain``
/
``retain_mut``
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10875] disallowed duplicated columns in table literals
IanManske 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10915] reduced element shifting in 
``Record::retain_mut``
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10900] made 
``FromValue``
 take owned 
``Value``
s
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10894] reused 
``Closure``
 type in 
``Value::Closure``
lavafroth implemented a few fixes for completions: 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10898] 1
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10831] 2
WindSoilder 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10852] introduced a 
``gen_save_call``
 function to reduce duplicate code
